title: Morgz' Career Is Completely Dead. What Happened?

media:group.media:title: Morgz' Career Is Completely Dead. What Happened?
media:group.media:description:
Back in 2019, Morgz was being talked about by every single YouTuber from Cody Ko to the Sidemen to PewDiePie, in the process finding himself in a beef with MrBeast. However, over the past few years, things have changed dramatically. Morgz' viewership has fallen from over 100 million per month to around 5 million per month, creating a question of "what on earth happened?"

This is, Morgz' Career Is Completely Dead. What Happened?
